RPi:

For boot options, change to boot to text console, auto login as pi
by editing /etc/systemd/system/autologin@.service
adding ExecStart just after [Service]:


[Service]
# the VT is cleared by TTYVTDisallocate
ExecStart=-/sbin/agetty --autologin pi  --noclear %I $TERM
Type=idle

